{"tid":2077032,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國鬥黃，香港有利！華爾街日報：中國籠絡共和黨，插足美國大選","createTime":"2020-06-24T03:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T05:14:14.000Z","uid":48040,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2a79c639a394f8494f3698ec7de361611945bf0b","tid":2077032,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T03:49:54.000Z","msg":"《華爾街日報》報導：<br />\n自特朗普當選以來，中國的有關人士就不斷投入數以十萬計的金錢以籠絡總統或共和黨，祈求特朗普再下一城獲得連任。中國以此插足美國大選，干預美國政策。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/political-donors-linked-to-china-won-access-to-trump-gop-11592925569?shareToken=st2b9c657e9b55454b9fdf6cf3df13fcf5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fpolitical-donors-linked-to-china-won-access-to-trump-gop-11592925569%3FshareToken%3Dst2b9c657e9b55454b9fdf6cf3df13fcf5&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=fbbcbc1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/political-donors-linked-to-china-won-access-to-trump-gop-11592925569?shareToken=st2b9c657e9b55454b9fdf6cf3df13fcf5</a><br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》呢篇報導攻擊特朗普以及共和黨。但大家唔駛激氣住。此報導可能掀起美國政壇的「鬥黃」。假如共和及民主黨以此作為戰場，兩黨不斷鬥黃，勢必令美國的外交政策更加強硬。<br />\n<br />\n======<br />\nTwitter戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1275636840188518403?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1275636840188518403%3Fs%3D20&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=59178940\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1275636840188518403%3Fs%3D20&h=440b1a87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1275636840188518403?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"2f206c8cbf90057ebec6d454858d02d3dfa74c4f","tid":2077032,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T03:54:27.000Z","msg":"借個位 會員標籤功能 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1880412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.